===Etymology===
Coined by Australian philosopher and researcher Glenn Albrecht of the roots {{etyl|la|en}} ''[[solacium|sōlācium]]'' ([[solace|comfort]]) and {{etyl|grc|en}} [[-algia|algia]] (pain).

===Noun===
{{en-noun|-}}

# (environmental change) A form of [[homesick]]ness one gets when one is still at home, but the [[environment]] is changed.
